The body of Heichel, 21, was found on Larch Mountain, a remote forested area east of Gresham, Police Chief Craig Junginger told a news conference. Whitney's 24-year-old neighbour Jonathan Holtwas arrested over the killing.

After collecting DNA and fingerprints and conducting three interviews over several days, police arrested Holt, who lived in the same apartment complex as Heichel and her husband.

