Holt, who knew Heichel and her husband, was arrested after police found inconsistencies in the stories that he told investigators over the course of two interviews.

Police said he is also tied to the crime by DNA evidence -- though they would not elaborate.

A motive for the horrific crime in unknown. Police did not comment on whether they have a theory of what led to the killing.

